    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This staff has 10 charges. While holding it, you can use an action to expend 1 or more of its charges to cast one of the following spells from it, using your spell save DC and spellcasting ability modifier: <em>@UUID[Compendium.black-flag.spells.Item.NQvy34IRCNEJfwip]{cure wounds}</em> (1 charge per spell circle, up to 4th), <em>@UUID[Compendium.black-flag.spells.Item.Aqff6XGGmiVXo6A6]{restoration}</em> (2 charges), or <em>@UUID[Compendium.black-flag.spells.Item.qGHh25GoYwwQ13NO]{mass cure wounds}</em> (5 charges).</p><p>The staff regains [[/r 1d6 + 4]] expended charges daily at dawn. If you expend the last charge, roll a d20. On a 1, the staff vanishes in a flash of light, lost forever.</p>",
